<plot>Based on real facts, this story portrays the physical and emotional isolation of two individuals and the futility of their attempt to escape it. Joyce Mattox, a woman engulfed by the boredom and mediocrity of her small-town existence, meets a prisoner on a visit with her church choir. Their attraction grows until Joyce is convinced that she must help Jesse break out of prison so that they can always be together.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?581032</url></doc>
